Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it that you want to do? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time I was asked that {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I looked up at the blue sky {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The answer is only in my heart {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't easily say the\Nwords that are really important{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I start running towards\Nthe place the light points to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:01:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's so much in my heart\Nthat I want to embrace, I could cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.27,0:01:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll keep painting my way,\NI promise, take it someday{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon,\Nwhere the white clouds drift{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The future is lined up and\Nit'll always be there by my side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Help... Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"My Amazing Stage Debut!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the city where Kaleido Stage is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to pass today's\Naudition no matter what
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and become a member of Kaleido Stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will! I will! I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, which way is Kaleido Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. Am I like totally lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's a newsstand.\NI'll go ask over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, is Kaleido Stage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:03:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got good, tight muscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't change the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck else should\NI watch out for, except you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like your suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mine now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maximum speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use these!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's how you're going to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, move it, move it,\Nmove it, move it! Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking this back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are always a lot\Nof runaways in this season.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't run away from home.\NI just got here from Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare to see runaways from so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I didn't run away from home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to be late for\Nthe audition! What'll I do?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the very least... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of how your\Nparents must be worrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just doing warm-up exercises.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, you came to\Naudition for Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I don't look it, but\NI'm a huge fan of Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy for you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, we can see it now.\NThat's Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! I'm really late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So, we will be announcing the results \Nfrom the judges after the matinee...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is it here? Or over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Or over here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank goodness! This is the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora! My name is Sora Naegino!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am very sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the auditions ended just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I came all this way\Nfrom Japan for this audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really? Okay,\Nthen come up on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The auditions are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Layla Hamilton... It's really her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's a reason for \Nwhy I was late and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens,\Na stage production begins on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just go home like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I absolutely,\Ndesperately want to join Kaleido Stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Miss Layla says no, then it's no, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:07:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back and try out next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a promise with my mom and dad
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I would give up if I failed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I was a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's been my dream to \Nperform in Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The show is going to start soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, you can stay and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's about all I can do for you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm Ken. Nice to meet you, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you join because you fell\Nin love with Kaleido Stage too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually wanted to be a cast\Nmember, but I have a weak heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I decided I would provide\Nsupport from behind the scenes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and got into the\Nmanagement side of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish I could have stood on this stage too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My arm got twisted!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to touch the\Nstage sets because it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one that's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go on stage now! Call the doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No means no! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We've got a problem. I need a\Ntrampoline cast member right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:36.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What the heck are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fill the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way an amateur can\Nperform in a real show right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what she said?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.87,0:11:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's not your place to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or am I in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is up to you to determine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I just have to think\Nof this as my audition, and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A doll is talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What incredible composure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.46,0:12:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she just twisted it.\NShe'll be fine by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She always blows things out of proportion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he pick that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could he possibly be thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it one of Kalos's whims?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here she comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the girl who was late to the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to be appearing\Nin the trampoline show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take off that costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being on stage is not so easy\Nthat an amateur can just fill the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you that I can do it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told her to do the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The performance is\Njust like I told you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot. What am\NI supposed to do first again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she'll be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! A flip! Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, no! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't do it! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't perform at all! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Rabbit, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't say that I can't do it. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to do it right now. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to do it! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if she could just nail the finale...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see below...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep smiling until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Good work out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad for you that\Nit all ended without mishap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the crowd was pretty into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to be happy about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you make a fool of\Nyourself right before my show?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just so desperately... wanted\Nto join... Kaleido Stage and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why the audience had to\Nsee such a disgraceful performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand just how\Nnaive you were now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no place for you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Golden Phoenix... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla's big routine. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even in death, Juliet's love {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}continues to burn for\Neternity like the phoenix.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is what the Golden Phoenix is about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to that,\NI can't even flap my wings yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, wait! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You passed, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're passing a girl\Nwho didn't even audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, the audience\Nwill come here just to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's what Kalos said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure it is. Have confidence in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Besides, I'm happy that I don't\Nhave to say goodbye to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:27.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Policeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I passed! I was able to pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? I'm happy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had faith in you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.39,0:20:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, I'm your first fan, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the dormitory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get some rest for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really a part of it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure it's the same as\Nthe one in the dressing room...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you can see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It... It really talked...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.42,0:21:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Spirit of the Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit of the Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you're lonely, what do you do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never say you don't get any of that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sleep, play, flip through a magazine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you're lonely, you're lonely{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.59,0:22:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like always, invisible vibes fly\Naround the city today, tulututu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, the vector of my heart\Nis talking about so many reasons{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.85,0:22:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to be free and fly the skies{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't have space to spread my wings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have faith {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.46,0:22:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is a future yet to be shaped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.20,0:22:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And there's a me that I want to shape{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.88,0:22:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I'm sad, even if it's a mistake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.34,0:22:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll do what I want and\Nfly towards the freedom{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:46.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Kaleido Star"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let us see your Golden Phoenix. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.51,0:22:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to be trying Miss Layla's\Nbig routine, the Golden Phoenix!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.97,0:22:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Miss Layla's said she'll\Nhave my resignation if I can't do it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:23:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a difficult routine that expresses\NJuliet's passion as she flies into Romeo's arms.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.14,0:23:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone says Miss Layla is the\Nonly person who can pull it off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Darn it! I've come this far!\NI just gotta do it! Gotta! Gotta! Gotta!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star,\N"My Amazing and Lonely Challenge!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream\Nand on towards the sky...{\i0}
